General.Name: Shanghai Wisdom Information Technology Co. Ltd.
General.Description: Shanghai Wisdom Information Technology Co., Ltd. engages in the software development business in China. Its products portfolio includes manufacturing operations management systems, enterprise resource management systems, IT integrated operation management platforms, and data management systems. The company also provides software production; application operation and maintenance services, such as failure reporting, troubleshooting, defect repair, routine inspections, installation, deployment, migration of application systems, operation and maintenance service reports, adaptation guarantee, and support and operation training services; and system operation and maintenance services, including platform operation monitoring, fault handling, application system data migration, data backup, upgrade and maintenance, and system layer software upgrade and maintenance, etc. In addition, it offers system integration services, which include construction of IT basic platform related to the operation of application software systems, such as server and network platform equipment, technical selection, procurement, installation, commissioning, integration, and training services of IT software and hardware, as well as data acquisition equipment, instrumentation, and various industrial robots. Further, the company provides software product sales and services primarily focuses on data processing and big data-related products and services, such as database software, big data platform software, big data tool software, etc. It offers its products for industrial intelligent manufacturing, digital finance, and various other applications. Shanghai Wisdom Information Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 2001 and is based in Shanghai, China.
